org.atmosphere.cpr

Class Action

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.atmosphere.cpr.Action

  • public final class Action
extends Object
    An Action is used by AtmosphereInterceptor, AsyncSupport and AtmosphereFramework to determine what to do with a request, e.g suspend it, resume it, etc.
